//label(scale(0.8)*"$23$",(63,45));
//label(scale(0.8)*"$17$", (70, 15));
[/asy] Since 36 people brought yoga mats and 20 of those people brought water bottles too, $36-20=16$ of the people have yoga mats but not water bottles.  Likewise, $26-20=6$ people brought water bottles but not yoga mats. [asy]
label("Yoga Mat", (2,75));
label("Water Bottle", (80,75));
draw(Circle((30,45), 22));
draw(Circle((58, 45), 22));
